org.knime.base.data.aggregation

Class NamedAggregationOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.base.data.aggregation.AggregationMethodDecorator
      • org.knime.base.data.aggregation.NamedAggregationOperator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<AggregationMethod>, AggregationMethod, AggregationFunctionRow<AggregationMethod>, AggregationFunction

    public class NamedAggregationOperator
extends AggregationMethodDecorator
    Combines a method with the name to use for this method. It is used in the Column Aggregator node which allows to specify a set of aggregation methods for a selected list of columns.
    Since:
    2.6
    Author:
    Tobias Koetter, University of Konstanz
